    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT:</h2><br><br><strong>CODING ROBO</strong> is an educational game that teaches the basics of programming and algorithmic logic. It introduces the notions of sequential programming, loops and conditions. No prior knowledge of programming is required to play.<br><br>Our robots have been lost on this planet. Your mission is to bring them back!<br>Robots can be controlled by sending commands. Give your instructions, solve coding puzzles and send robots back to the earth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 30 unique levels<br></li><li> Challenging coding puzzles<br></li><li> Block-based programming<br></li><li> Tutorials<br></li><li> Level editor</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2>Level Editor allows you to create your own levels with everything in CODING ROBO. You can create, share it with other players or even play/rate other levels created by players around the world.<br><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297880/extras/652014a76cbb150825251798eb9d83ab.poster.avif?t=1726516231\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297880/extras/652014a76cbb150825251798eb9d83ab.webm?t=1726516231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297880/extras/652014a76cbb150825251798eb9d83ab.mp4?t=1726516231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
